  "texts": [
    "The formulation of a comparative schema for a CMER system, demonstrating its applicability across a diverse range of use-cases, promoting its practical relevance and addressing the potential challenges (Sect. 7, answer to RQ3).",
    "A thorough investigation into the ethical implications of CMER systems, providing insights into data protection, privacy issues, and methods to address biases.",
    "This includes the proposal of key principles concerning ethics and privacy, framing guidelines for ethical CMER applications (Sect. 8, answer to RQ4).",
    "A detailed analysis of the current limitations, potential remedial measures, and emerging trends in the CMER landscape, providing guidance for future research and development in the field (Sect. 9, answer to RQ5).This study elucidates both the general principles of MER and the specifics of its contactless variant.",
    "It explores the roles of various modalities and their associated cues in emotion recognition, highlighting their advantages and disadvantages."
